'''Ahmed Mostafa Mohamed Sayed''' ({{langx|ar|أحمد مصطفى محمد سيد}}; born 10 January 1996) commonly known as '''Zizo''' ({{langx|ar|زيزو}}), is an Egyptian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Winger (association football)|winger]] for [[Egyptian Premier League]] club [[Al Ahly SC|Al Ahly]] and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].

==Club career==
===Early life and career===
Zizo made his [[Belgian First Division A|Belgian Pro League]] debut at 29 March 2014 against [[Waasland-Beveren]] in a 0–2 away win in the [[2013–14 Belgian Pro League|2013–14]] season, he replaced [[Souleymane Diomandé]] after 50 minutes.<ref name="soccerway2">{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2014/03/29/belgium/pro-league/kv-red-star-waasland/koninklijke-lierse-sportkring/1661632/|title=Waasland-Beveren vs. Lierse - 29 March 2014 - Soccerway|publisher=soccerway.com|accessdate=16 August 2014}}</ref> He went onto make 72 appearances and score 49 goals in his first four seasons between 2014 and 2017 with [[Lierse S.K. (1906)|Lierse]].<ref name="soccerway"/> In January 2017, Sayed joined [[Primeira Liga]] side [[C.D. Nacional|Nacional]] on loan, with an option to buy, for the rest of the 2016–17 season.<ref name="Joined Nacional 1">{{cite news|title=Nacional e Lierse acordam cedência de Zizo|url=http://www.cdnacional.pt/nacional-lierse-acordam-cedencia-zizo/|accessdate=22 January 2017|work=C.D. Nacional|date=22 January 2017}}</ref>

=== Zamalek ===
[[File:Zizo zsc.jpg|thumb|upright|Zizo playing for [[Zamalek SC|Zamalek]] in 2025]]

In January 2019, Zizo returned to Egypt, signing for [[Zamalek SC|Zamalek]], after one and a half seasons at [[Moreirense F.C.|Moreirense]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.jmgfootball.com/en/2019/02/01/zamalek-sign-egyptian-winger-ahmed-sayed-from-portugals-moreirense/ |title=Zamalek sign Egyptian winger Ahmed Sayed from Portugal's Moreirense |publisher=JMG Football |date=1 February 2019 }}</ref> He achieved with the White Castle the [[Egyptian Premier League]] twice in ([[2020–21 Egyptian Premier League|2020–21]], [[2021–22 Egyptian Premier League|2021–22]]), the [[Egypt Cup]] in ([[2018–19 Egypt Cup|2018–19]], [[2020–21 Egypt Cup|2020–21]], [[2024–25 Egypt Cup|2024–25]]), and the [[Egyptian Super Cup]] once in ([[2019–20 Egyptian Super Cup|2019–20]]). On the continental level, Zizo won with Zamalek the [[CAF Confederation Cup]] twice in ([[2018–19 CAF Confederation Cup|2018–19]], [[2023–24 CAF Confederation Cup|2023–24]]), and the [[CAF Super Cup]] twice in ([[2020 CAF Super Cup (February)|2020]], [[2024 CAF Super Cup|2024]]).

=== Al Ahly ===
On 6 June 2025, it was officially announced that Zizo would join [[Al Ahly SC|Al Ahly]] on a four-year deal, following the expiration of his contract with [[Zamalek SC|Zamalek]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.kingfut.com/2025/06/06/official-al-ahly-sign-ahmed-sayed-zizo-on-a-free-transfer/ |title=OFFICIAL: Al Ahly Sign Ahmed Sayed Zizo on a Free Transfer |date=6 June 2025 |website=KingFut |accessdate=5 August 2025}}</ref> He became eligible to compete with Al Ahly in the [[2025 FIFA Club World Cup]]. Furious fans of his previous club named him "the hungry" ({{langx|ar|الجعان}}), as he left his home club who actually created his stardom in football,<ref>{{Cite web |title=أحمد صالح: الزمالك صنع اسم زيزو.. واللاعب لازم يضحي {{!}} المصري اليوم |url=https://www.almasryalyoum.com/news/details/3369011 |access-date=2025-10-06 |website=www.almasryalyoum.com |language=ar}}</ref> and went for Zamalek's rival for a higher contract.<ref>{{Cite web |last=الزمان |date=2025-09-29 |title=جماهير الزمالك تهاجم زيزو قبل القمة: «واحد اتنين.. الجعان فين؟» {{!}} رياضة {{!}} الزمان |url=https://www.elzmannews.com/512111 |access-date=2025-10-06 |website=www.elzmannews.com |language=ar}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2025/4/11/%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%B1%D9%81-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%8A%D9%84-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84%D8%A9-%D9%84%D8%B9%D9%82%D8%AF-%D8%A3%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF-%D9%85%D8%B5%D8%B7%D9%81%D9%89-%D8%B2%D9%8A%D8%B2%D9%88-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%87%D9%84%D9%89/6949873|title=تعرف على التفاصيل الكاملة لعقد أحمد مصطفى زيزو مع الأهلى|date=11 April 2025|website=اليوم السابع}}</ref>

== International career ==
[[File:Ahmed Sayed (Zizo).jpg|thumb|upright|Zizo with [[Egypt national football team|Egypt]] at the [[2021 Africa Cup of Nations final]]]]

On 4 December 2021, Zizo scored his first goal with the [[Egypt national football team|Egyptian national team]] during a group stage match against [[Sudan national football team|Sudan]] in the [[2021 FIFA Arab Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2021/12/4/%D8%B2%D9%8A%D8%B2%D9%88-%D9%8A%D8%B3%D8%AC%D9%84-%D9%87%D8%AF%D9%81%D9%87-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%88%D9%84-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D9%85%D8%B5%D8%B1-%D9%81%D9%89-%D9%85%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%87/5565459|title=زيزو يسجل هدفه الدولى الأول مع منتخب مصر فى مباراته الثامنة|date=4 December 2021|website=اليوم السابع}}</ref>

On 2 December 2025, Zizo was called up to the Egypt squad for the [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cafonline.com/afcon2025/news/egypt-name-final-28-man-squad-for-totalenergies-caf-afcon-2025-salah-leads-pharaohs-charge/|title=Egypt name final 28-man squad for TotalEnergies CAF AFCON 2025, Salah leads Pharaohs' charge|publisher=[[Confederation of African Football]]|date=2 December 2025|access-date=12 December 2025}}</ref>

== Personal life ==
He was married on 4 August 2019, and has two daughters.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.masrawy.com/sports/sports-others/details/2024/12/16/2692892/20-%D8%B5%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%B5%D8%AF-%D9%82%D8%B5%D8%A9-%D8%AD%D8%A8-%D8%A3%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF-%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%AF-%D8%B2%D9%8A%D8%B2%D9%88-%D9%88%D8%B2%D9%88%D8%AC%D8%AA%D9%87-|title=20 صورة ترصد قصة حب أحمد سيد زيزو وزوجته|website=مصراوي.كوم}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2025/10/14/%D8%B2%D9%8A%D8%B2%D9%88-%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%87%D9%84%D9%8A-%D9%88%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D9%85%D8%B5%D8%B1-%D9%8A%D9%8F%D8%B1%D8%B2%D9%82-%D8%A8%D9%85%D9%88%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AF%D8%AA%D9%87-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AB%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%B5%D9%88%D9%81%D9%8A%D8%A7-%D8%B5%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%A9/7156512|title=زيزو نجم الأهلي ومنتخب مصر يُرزق بمولودته الثانية "صوفيا"..صورة|first=لبنى|last=عبد الله|date=14 October 2025|website=اليوم السابع}}</ref>

